* {{cite news |author=Lyons, Richard D. |date=April 22, 1968 |title=Ultimate Speck appeal may cite a genetic defect |newspaper=[[The New York Times]] |page=43 |url=http://select.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=F20C10FA355D147493C0AB178FD85F4C8685F9}}
