* {{cite journal |author=. |date=May 18, 1970 |title=Congenital criminals? |magazine=[[Newsweek]] |volume=75 |issue=20 |pages=98–99}}
* {{cite book |author=Katz, Jay; Capron, Alexander Morgan; Glass, Eleanor Swift |year=1972 |title=Experimentation with human beings; the authority of the investigator, subject, professions, and state in the human experimentation process |pages=342–346 |location=New York |publisher=[[Russell Sage Foundation]] |isbn=0-87154-438-5}}
