* {{cite news|author=Bruzelius, Nils|date=December 15, 1974|title=Harvard Medical School panel rejects plea to end gene study|newspaper=[[The Boston Globe]]|page=8|url=http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/boston/access/2056634312.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:AI}}
